    Don't handle back key twice
    
    The back key is also handled by a shortcut handler a few lines down,
    together with the forward key.
    
    This fixes a double page pop when pressing the back key (or using the
    back gesture) on Android.
    
    This went unnoticed as one of those didn't actually work, but Qt 6.11
    apparently fixed this, breaking applications with a page stack depth > 1.

